Author: (Nyl. ex Malbr.) A. Nordin, S. Savic & Tibel
Notes: Appears to have been incorrectly accessioned as Rinodina caesiocinerea
Previously erroneously reported as Sphaerophorus globiferus (L.) DC. var. gracilis Müll. Arg. = Sphaerophorus globosus (Hudson)
Laetiporus sulphureus is previously reported by R. Zich, however that species is limited to eastern North America
European species; not certain to be present in NA
